 it doesn=E2=80=99t pay particularly well. So you can afford to go do somet=
hing else, because it wouldn=E2=80=99t be that big a pay cut from your Wall=
 Street job anyway, and it would be more pleasant.=C2=A0When business is=C2=
=A0good, your job is exciting but you work too hard and get burned out, and=
 then you get a giant bonus at the end of the year. So you can afford to go=
