und-color: #ccc;">her Forbes contributor page</a>.</p><p style=3D"margin: 1=
6px 0;">In her private life=C2=A0she allegedly <a href=3D"https://link.mail=
.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26652347.266610/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLm=
NvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDItMDgvZG9qLXNlaXplcy0zLTYtYmlsbGlvbi1pbi1ia=
